'''Grutchin carriers''' were [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] used by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. They were nearly identical to [[Yorik-et|coralskippers]], except they trailed 'tails' that bled [[grutchin]]s and countermeasures. To get close enough, they were used in strafing runs on [[Capital ship/Legends|capital ships]], often on suicide missions when the Vong would hold back other starfighters.

